  grand rapids , michigan hosts a " pulaski days " celebration annually on the first full weekend of october in recognition of general pulaski and the polish culture in general.http://www.pulaskidays.org/objectives.htm   in popular culture michigan - born songwriter sufjan stevens titled a song " casimir pulaski day " on his album illinois .

holidays & observances : casimir pulaski day , the first monday in march , celebrates a revolutionary war hero born in this country

